data.description: Gorgeous painted brick exterior welcomes you home to this upgraded 5 BR,4 Bath home w 5 Living Areas & extended covered patio w Outdoor Fireplace! Lots of windows & natural light! Private Study off Foyer. Open flex plan w 2 BRs down- Main & Guest BRs. Big Open Kitchen w island, wlkin pantry, gas cooktop & pot-filler. 2-story Family Rm features corner gas-log FirePlc & window views to covered patio & outdoor fireplace- a perfect spot for morning coffee or a glass of wine in the evening! Big backyard w wood privacy fence & room to play or build a pool! Private Main BR has luxe bath w 2 sinks-vanities,garden tub,sep.shower & wlkin closet that connects w large Laundry Rm w lots of bltin storage.  Stunning modern turned staircase leads up to 3 BRs,2 full baths,Game,Media & Play Rms! Enjoy Sandbrock Ranch amenities- pool, splash pad, playground, treehouse, fitness center, dog park & more! 3 car tandem garage! New Sandbrock Ranch Elementary School! Denton ISD. This is HOME!
